title: Episode 294: Lazy P*ssy (Feat. Blac Chyna)
itunes:title: Episode 294: Lazy P*ssy (Feat. Blac Chyna)
description:
Singer/entrepreneur Blac Chyna, joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her new CBD line, as well as her latest single "Doom" featuring Asian Doll. The ladies discuss a range of topics including co-parenting, lazy sex, time management when your life is busy and much more. Enjoy!
